#: Game.Levels.SetWorld.L08_CompoundPredicate
msgid "# Compound Predicates\n"
"\n"
"So far, each set predicate has tested a single condition. But predicates\n"
"can combine conditions using logical connectives.\n"
"\n"
"The set §0 contains even numbers less than 10:\n"
"the set §1.\n"
"\n"
"Membership unfolds to the conjunction: §2\n"
"becomes §3. To prove a conjunction, you split it with\n"
"§4 and prove each part separately.\n"
"\n"
"The proof strategy:\n"
"1. §5 — split §6 into two goals\n"
"2. Prove §7 with §8\n"
"3. Prove §9 by providing the witness §10 (since §11)\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove that 6 belongs to the set of even numbers less than 10."
msgstr ""

