#: Game.Levels.SubsetWorld.L13_Antisymm
msgid "# An Alternative Route to Set Equality\n"
"\n"
"In Levels 10–11, you proved set equalities using §0 — reducing to\n"
"a membership biconditional and proving both directions.\n"
"\n"
"There is another route: **double containment** (also called\n"
"**antisymmetry**). If §1 AND §2, then §3.\n"
"\n"
"The theorem §4 captures this:\n"
"\n"
"§5\n"
"\n"
"If you already have two subset proofs, you can combine them with\n"
"§6 to get equality directly — no\n"
"§7 needed.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Given §8 and §9, prove §10."
msgstr ""

