msgid "# Chaining Subsets\n"
"\n"
"If §0 and §1, then §2. This is\n"
"**transitivity** of the subset relation.\n"
"\n"
"In Level 6, you learned that a subset hypothesis §3 acts as\n"
"a function: given a proof that §4, it returns a proof that\n"
"§5. Now you will **chain** two such function applications to\n"
"prove transitivity.\n"
