msgid "# Boss: Intersection Distributes over Union\n"
"\n"
"Time to integrate everything. Prove the **distributive law** for sets:\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"This says: being in §1 AND in §2 is the same as being in\n"
"§3 OR in §4. It is the set-theoretic version of the\n"
"propositional identity §5.\n"
"\n"
"**Skills required** (all taught in this world):\n"
