#: Game.Levels.SetOpsWorld.L15_DoubleComplement
msgid "You proved §0 — double complementation is the identity.\n"
"\n"
"The forward direction is pure **double negation elimination**: from\n"
"§1, conclude §2. This required §3 (classical logic),\n"
"just like the complement union law in the previous level.\n"
"\n"
