"§1\n"
"\n"
"## Syntax\n"
"§2\n"
"\n"
"## When to use it\n"
"When you have (or can prove) both §3 and §4 and want to\n"
"conclude §5. This is the \\\\\"double containment\\\\\" proof strategy.\n"
"\n"
"## Example\n"
"§6"
msgstr ""

