msgid "You used §0 to convert the goal, then §1 to close it.\n"
"\n"
"The chain of definitional reductions that §2 verified:\n"
"1. §3 — the original statement\n"
"2. §4 — notation expansion\n"
"3. §5 — membership is function application\n"
"4. §6 — beta reduction\n"
"\n"
"**§7 is a general tool**, not just an arithmetic trick. It works\n"
"whenever two expressions are *definitionally equal* — meaning Lean can\n"
