#: Game.Levels.SubsetWorld.L01_FirstSubset
msgid "# Subsets: The ⊆ Relation\n"
"\n"
"In mathematics, §0 means every element of §1 is also an\n"
"element of §2. In Lean, this is exactly what it means:\n"
"\n"
"§3\n"
"\n"
"So a subset proof has the shape: **introduce** an arbitrary element §4\n"
"and a hypothesis §5 that §6, then **show** that §7.\n"
"\n"
"After §8, you will have:\n"
"- §9 — this is §10 wrapped in set notation\n"
"- Goal: §11 — this is §12 wrapped in set notation\n"
"\n"
"Both are wrapped in set notation. You already know §13 for\n"
"converting the goal to an equivalent form — use §14 to\n"
"unwrap the goal. For the hypothesis, you can use §15 to extract\n"
"the arithmetic: §16 creates a clean arithmetic\n"
"hypothesis that §17 can read.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
