"§5 *destructs* a pair (splits §6 into\n"
"its components). In this proof you saw the dual: §7\n"
"*constructs* a pair — it builds a conjunction from two pieces already\n"
"in context. Think of §8 as anonymous pair notation: §9\n"
"takes it apart, §10 puts it together."
